OL,3,CCCTV appeal after #10,000 of golf
OL,4,Cclubs stolen from golf club
OL,6,FPolice in Hampshire have released an
OL,7,Fimage of two people they want to speak
OL,8,Fwith in connection with the theft of
OL,9,Fgolf clubs worth more than #10,000.
OL,11,FTwo people, a man and woman - are
OL,12,Freported to have each stolen a set of
OL,13,Fclubs from the Royal Winchester Golf
OL,14,FCourse on Sarum Road on Tuesday
OL,15,Fafternoon. (14 April)
OL,17,FThe are described as a white man, aged
OL,18,Fbetween 30 and 45-years-old, with a
OL,19,Fslim build. He was wearing blue jeans,
OL,20,Fa black jacket, white trainers, and a
OL,21,Fbaseball cap.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
