OL,3,CCCTV appeal after #10,000 of golf
OL,4,Cclubs stolen from golf club
OL,6,FA white woman, aged between 30 and 45-
OL,7,Fyears-old, with a large build. She was
OL,8,Fwearing black leggings, a black
OL,9,Fjacket, black trainers, and a blue
OL,10,Fbaseball cap.
OL,12,FOfficers believe the pair left in a
OL,13,Fred car.
OL,15,FA Hampshire Police spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"Do you recognise them?
OL,18,F"Perhaps you were there at the time
OL,19,Fand witnessed something?
